In the dealtime, you can be reminder
that almost no policy position of a president in a iacultyoriented institution
like this one will have its intended effect on the community unless you stand
by it. in a very real sense, not only
the academic direction but also the act
comic and non-academic order of this
College tests in both your hands and
mine. The way by which we work together, talk over our differences nationally, and above all, discharge our teaching and other professional obligations is
the basic style that supports or weekend the whole character of this Col
legs. With students as sensitive and intelligent as ours, our real if unexpressed
